OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining cloud and rain soon clearing
OL,7,Feast. Otherwise largely dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells through the night, but the odd
OL,9,Fshower feeding in from the west.
OL,10,FOccasionally blustery southwest winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FIt will be largely dry with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells, though with
OL,14,Fthe chance of the odd shower. Cloudier
OL,15,Fevening with some patchy rain. A bit
OL,16,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
