OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FQuite
OL,6,Fcloudy Saturday morning with some
OL,7,Frain, drier and brighter later.
OL,8,FCloudy, fresh southerly winds, and
OL,9,Foccasional outbreaks of rain on Sunday
OL,10,Fand Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
